Reviews: Liked product will buy again
It's quite compact ,works better than the cheapest one's I've been using.It dose have a short stalk between  Handel and ground but it sprayed my 1200sm block fine.Highly recommend this sprayer.

I've had cheaper brands from Bunnings that just didn't cut it - they were either too big and heavy, didn't pump well, easily clogged etc. This one is perfect. Not too heavy carry when full (I use it to poison weeds in driveway, paths and paved verandah). Easy to use. Definitely recommend.

The Hills 100728 5 litre Garden Sprayer is a well made unit that has done everything I've asked it to do.
The Sprayer is easy to assemble and worked perfectly straight away. I have used one of this model prior to this and it proved reliable and efficient.
